<li><i><a href="/wiki/Chhoti_Si_Baat" title="Chhoti Si Baat">Chhoti Si Baat</a></i> - A 1975 (Hindi) Indian film. Asrani riding a yellow Vespa 150 in many shots in the movie.</li>
